                          "bold": false
                        }
                      ],
                      {
                        "text": "Mine Treasure is designed to add chance to Minecraft's mining. Mining stone-related blocks will give the player the possibility to find a treasure. These treasures differ in rarity and types such as tiers and biome-specific loot.",
                        "color": "black",
                        "italic": false
                      },
                      [
                        {
                          "text": "Common Treasure:\n",
                          "color": "#8C817E",
                          "italic": false
                        },
                        {
                          "text": "Has the highest chance to spawn. Meaning it is the most common out of any Treasure. The loot contained in them is very basic and mediocre. Their convenience comes in an easier way of obtaining common resources.",
                          "color": "black"
                        }
                      ],
                      [
                        {
                          "text": "Rare Treasure:\n",
                          "color": "blue",
                          "italic": false
                        },
                        {
                          "text": "Has a lower chance to spawn. Contains decent loot such as tools, armor, and other utilities which are quite useful. These can hold quite powerful items if the player is lucky enough to stumble upon them.",
                          "color": "black"
                        }
                      ],
                      [
                        {
                          "text": "Epic Treasure:\n",
                          "color": "red",
                          "italic": false
                        },
                        {
                          "text": "Has a slim chance to spawn. The loot is reaching end-game levels of strength. Extremely useful items and utilities can be found in these treasures. Potentially changing the game for the player who finds one.",
                          "color": "black"
                        }
                      ],
                      [
                        {
                          "text": "Legendary Treasure:\n",
                          "color": "gold",
                          "italic": false
                        },
                        {
                          "text": "Has a really low chance to spawn. The best tier of loot one could imagine. Powerful weapons, armor, and utility items which determine the outcome in any fight. If one is lucky enough to find one, they have a severe advantage.",
                          "color": "black"
                        }
                      ],
                      [
                        {
                          "text": "Mythical Treasure:\n",
                          "color": "light_purple",
                          "italic": false
