                          "text": "Stone-types:\n",
                          "bold": true,
                          "italic": false
                        },
                        {
                          "text": "Stone-types are extremely important in Mine Treasure. They have different treasure spawn rates.\n\nStone:\nCommon: 1%\nRare: 0.25%\nEpic: 0.032%\nLegendary: 0.016%\nMythical: 0.008%",
                          "bold": false
                        }
                      ],
                      {
                        "text": "Granite: Higher epic rates at the cost of lower common and rare\nDiorite: Higher common rates, but lower epic and rare\nAndesite/Magma Block: Higher rare, lower common and epic\nOres: Higher everything"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": "Deepslate/End Stone: Higher everything\nDeepslate Ore: Even higher\nDiamond Ore: Highest possible chance for everything. Strategy is to instamine Stone ASAP and try to find an Efficiency 9+ Pickaxe in the Deep Dark or Mountain."
